WEBVTT

01:50.240 --> 01:53.930
[Love Between Lines]

01:54.310 --> 01:56.789
[Episode 2]

02:02.570 --> 02:06.330
♪ What identity do you use
to enter and exit the role? ♪

02:07.330 --> 02:11.650
♪ Reality and fantasy
are parallel and intertwine ♪

02:12.370 --> 02:16.240
♪ About the characters
and relationships of love ♪

02:13.750 --> 02:15.610
Everyone, welcome to Rongcheng.

02:16.310 --> 02:17.560
The blizzard has blocked the roads.

02:17.230 --> 02:21.940
♪  Like a multifaceted gem,
obsessed with each side ♪

02:17.750 --> 02:19.030
Distinguished guests,

02:19.030 --> 02:21.630
you'll have to
temporarily stay in Rongcheng.

02:22.170 --> 02:27.090
♪ Time and space interlace;
it's still you ♪

02:27.120 --> 02:31.360
♪ Love overlaps in destiny ♪

02:28.450 --> 02:32.160
[15 minutes ago]

02:31.390 --> 02:35.950
♪ You made me change
my impromptu promise ♪

02:35.980 --> 02:40.820
♪ Two hearts slowly get closer
amidst sparks ♪

02:37.470 --> 02:39.190
This is exactly what I needed.

02:39.190 --> 02:40.079
Anna,

02:40.079 --> 02:41.810
financial advisor from Side M.

02:41.840 --> 02:43.310
Your mission in Rongcheng

02:43.310 --> 02:44.430
is to help Qin Xiaoyi

02:44.430 --> 02:46.400
become the new mayor of Rongcheng

02:46.400 --> 02:47.840
and gain his trust.

02:47.960 --> 02:49.840
You must beat others

02:49.840 --> 02:50.870
in convincing Qin Xiaoyi

02:50.870 --> 02:52.630
to sign the policy contract.

02:52.750 --> 02:53.680
However,

02:53.680 --> 02:55.680
you have a secret past.

02:55.800 --> 02:56.800
A few years ago,

02:56.800 --> 02:58.800
you were saved by Ning Zechen.

02:58.910 --> 02:59.840
In order to repay him,

02:59.840 --> 03:01.190
your real mission

03:01.190 --> 03:03.630
is to help Ning Zechen become the mayor.

03:03.880 --> 03:06.080
The box of rouge
is your token of recognition.

03:06.080 --> 03:08.310
He will provide evidence
to frame Qin Xiaoyi.

03:08.160 --> 03:11.480
♪ To heal each other ♪

03:08.310 --> 03:10.030
But your identity as a mole

03:10.030 --> 03:11.750
must not be discovered by Qin Xiaoyi.

03:11.750 --> 03:13.410
Please proceed with caution.

03:37.750 --> 03:38.680
Let's go.

03:43.800 --> 03:44.630
Who are you?

03:45.560 --> 03:47.120
Let's talk, Chief Ning.

03:56.470 --> 03:57.560
You're Anna.

03:59.590 --> 04:01.190
Long time no see, Chief Ning.

04:01.960 --> 04:03.560
It's such an old thing.

04:03.800 --> 04:05.600
I'm surprised you still have it.

04:06.000 --> 04:06.560
Anna,

04:06.870 --> 04:08.280
have you been well abroad

04:09.120 --> 04:10.470
these past years?

04:11.150 --> 04:13.240
I have to put on this reunion act?

04:16.390 --> 04:17.450
I've been alright.

04:19.360 --> 04:21.600
Ten years since we parted.

04:21.870 --> 04:22.930
On life's journey,

04:23.270 --> 04:26.120
we meet again.

04:26.480 --> 04:27.600
Oh please!

04:27.600 --> 04:29.430
Why are you reciting poetry now?

04:31.040 --> 04:34.920
Let bygones be bygones.

04:40.070 --> 04:41.360
W-What does that mean?

04:42.800 --> 04:44.070
It means

04:44.100 --> 04:45.930
"move on from the past."

04:46.430 --> 04:48.830
Hurry and give me
the evidence to frame Qin Xiaoyi.

04:48.830 --> 04:51.030
Only then can we move forward together.

04:52.270 --> 04:54.130
So, stop talking and give it to me.

05:00.040 --> 05:01.440
And give me a handgun too.

05:07.440 --> 05:08.220
Nothing else, right?

05:08.220 --> 05:08.870
Money.

05:12.190 --> 05:14.040
You're robbing me.

05:16.800 --> 05:17.600
Ms. Anna,

05:17.800 --> 05:19.480
I have high hopes for you,

05:19.630 --> 05:21.310
but if General Qin finds out about this,

05:21.310 --> 05:23.690
as the Police Chief, I cannot...

05:23.730 --> 05:24.410
Got it.

05:40.860 --> 05:45.540
[General's Office]

05:50.090 --> 05:50.550
Come in.

06:00.790 --> 06:02.650
I thought I'd acted early enough.

06:08.000 --> 06:10.270
Which side are you on?

06:12.430 --> 06:14.430
You're here to steal things.

06:14.430 --> 06:15.870
I'm here to plant things.

06:16.040 --> 06:16.970
Same objective.

06:17.390 --> 06:18.670
What are you talking about?

06:18.670 --> 06:21.380
We're each doing our own tasks.

06:21.410 --> 06:22.140
Understand?

06:22.480 --> 06:22.870
Listen.

06:22.870 --> 06:24.750
Don't tell anyone you've seen us.

06:25.430 --> 06:26.120
Fine.

06:26.610 --> 06:27.410
Okay.

06:33.920 --> 06:34.600
What?

06:35.150 --> 06:36.350
Qin Xiaoyi is coming?

06:36.770 --> 06:38.370
Okay, we'll leave right now.

06:38.630 --> 06:39.390
Okay, okay.

06:40.270 --> 06:41.070
Hey...

06:41.070 --> 06:42.560
Is it appropriate
to take out a phone here?

06:42.560 --> 06:43.070
Look.

06:43.530 --> 06:44.460
It's just a game.

06:44.490 --> 06:45.680
Don't take things so seriously.

06:45.680 --> 06:46.510
Let's go.

06:46.800 --> 06:47.390
Go!

07:02.720 --> 07:03.480
Stop!

07:05.750 --> 07:06.310
What?

07:07.140 --> 07:07.750
Let her go!

07:07.870 --> 07:08.260
I...

07:11.560 --> 07:12.220
After them!

07:12.310 --> 07:12.970
After them!

07:31.660 --> 07:32.590
General Qin,

07:32.950 --> 07:35.210
don't you know to secure your own things?

07:35.320 --> 07:37.030
Someone broke into your office
to steal files.

07:37.030 --> 07:37.909
I tried to help,

07:37.930 --> 07:39.340
and this is my outcome?

07:40.159 --> 07:41.000
I can see

07:41.159 --> 07:42.490
you've tried very hard.

07:42.720 --> 07:43.390
Thank you.

07:50.720 --> 07:51.920
No, I can do it myself.

07:53.600 --> 07:54.270
Of course.

08:07.840 --> 08:08.840
You two,

08:09.250 --> 08:10.960
go check my office.

08:11.150 --> 08:12.610
See if anything is missing

08:13.270 --> 08:14.040
or

08:14.940 --> 08:16.120
if anything new has appeared.

08:16.120 --> 08:16.690
Yes, sir.

08:26.030 --> 08:26.780
General,

08:27.310 --> 08:28.560
a document is missing,

08:28.560 --> 08:29.360
but

08:29.510 --> 08:30.970
nothing new has appeared.

08:36.539 --> 08:37.990
The office is so messy.

08:38.010 --> 08:39.940
He'll definitely tidy it up later.

08:40.240 --> 08:42.150
If I hide something here now,

08:42.390 --> 08:44.049
it'll be discovered quickly.

08:44.510 --> 08:46.310
Not only will I fail to frame him,

08:46.440 --> 08:48.500
but I'll become the suspect instead.

08:49.010 --> 08:49.920
Not bad.

08:50.270 --> 08:51.400
You dodged a bullet.

08:51.960 --> 08:52.870
General Qin,

08:53.440 --> 08:55.640
I don't know what you're talking about.

08:55.910 --> 08:57.320
I want to invite you

08:57.320 --> 08:58.320
to come in.

09:05.200 --> 09:06.260
Please have a seat.

09:13.240 --> 09:14.910
Wasn't your file stolen?

09:14.910 --> 09:16.710
Why aren't you going after them?

09:17.440 --> 09:18.080
There are

09:18.080 --> 09:20.210
no important documents to steal here.

09:21.600 --> 09:23.320
Everything's hidden elsewhere.

09:23.320 --> 09:24.720
How scheming.

09:28.270 --> 09:30.470
I'm complimenting your intelligence.

09:32.720 --> 09:34.600
Then why are you here?

09:40.920 --> 09:42.850
I'm a financial advisor for Side M.

09:43.120 --> 09:45.000
I'm here to discuss a partnership
with you.

09:45.000 --> 09:46.000
As long as

09:46.000 --> 09:47.460
you sign this contract...

09:49.320 --> 09:52.080
Once it's signed...

09:57.000 --> 09:58.720
And the contract is sent back to M,

09:58.720 --> 10:01.720
the promised funds
will be transferred immediately.

10:01.750 --> 10:02.870
General Qin, I know

10:03.080 --> 10:04.410
you want to be the mayor.

10:04.750 --> 10:06.000
I can help you.

10:10.870 --> 10:12.400
I understand what you mean,

10:13.120 --> 10:15.320
but if you want me to sign this contract,

10:15.630 --> 10:17.560
you need to show me your sincerity.

10:19.790 --> 10:21.550
What kind of sincerity?

10:23.610 --> 10:25.400
Is it still about that formula?

10:30.960 --> 10:31.840
Wait!

10:35.630 --> 10:36.480
General Qin,

10:36.770 --> 10:38.130
I know what you want.

10:41.450 --> 10:42.450
Tonight at 10,

10:42.550 --> 10:43.950
meet me at the dance hall.

10:44.590 --> 10:45.790
Everything is ready.

10:45.840 --> 10:47.030
You just need the final push.

10:47.030 --> 10:47.960
General Qin,

10:48.320 --> 10:49.390
I'll give you

10:49.750 --> 10:50.680
this final push.

11:01.750 --> 11:04.480
It seems all the plot missions
are pre-designed.

11:04.720 --> 11:07.240
I got the formula here last time too.

11:08.030 --> 11:09.360
So, I just need to...

11:09.600 --> 11:10.630
Stop, stop, stop!

11:10.790 --> 11:11.360
Stop!

11:11.870 --> 11:12.930
What are you doing?

11:13.610 --> 11:15.140
I'm robbing you of a letter!

11:22.950 --> 11:23.860
General Qin,

11:24.110 --> 11:25.920
may I have this dance?

11:26.040 --> 11:26.730
I'm sorry.

11:46.720 --> 11:49.450
Seems I've offered
the wrong token of sincerity.

11:49.860 --> 11:51.150
Ms. Anna.

12:00.390 --> 12:01.030
This

12:01.240 --> 12:03.840
contains the formula
for manufacturing arms.

12:03.960 --> 12:05.390
Before Sun Jiaying could get it,

12:05.390 --> 12:06.480
I intercepted it.

12:06.870 --> 12:07.790
General Qin,

12:07.790 --> 12:08.870
are you satisfied?

12:11.120 --> 12:12.250
As we agreed before,

12:12.390 --> 12:13.720
I show you my sincerity,

12:13.750 --> 12:15.610
and you sign the contract with me.

12:17.510 --> 12:18.510
It seems that you have

12:18.510 --> 12:20.440
some misunderstandings about me.

12:21.120 --> 12:21.790
I don't

12:22.000 --> 12:23.960
accept negotiations.

12:26.320 --> 12:28.120
Well, that's unfortunate then.

12:37.120 --> 12:38.200
General Qin,

12:38.200 --> 12:39.800
have you made your decision?

12:48.970 --> 12:51.030
General Qin, then I'll take my leave.

13:00.040 --> 13:00.840
Take her away.

13:04.530 --> 13:06.480
Qin Xiaoyi, you broke your promise!

13:06.480 --> 13:06.880
You...

13:09.040 --> 13:10.850
Did I ever promise you anything?

13:13.000 --> 13:13.750
I know

13:14.180 --> 13:16.640
there are spies around me
planted by others.

13:18.960 --> 13:19.510
Hey,

13:19.840 --> 13:20.750
if you don't trust me,

13:20.750 --> 13:22.270
why ask me for the formula?

13:23.010 --> 13:24.130
All's fair in war.

13:25.310 --> 13:26.270
Besides,

13:26.600 --> 13:27.600
what you gave me

13:28.010 --> 13:30.210
probably isn't the real formula, is it?

13:40.050 --> 13:42.290
[Those who seek revenge are gentlemen]

13:47.510 --> 13:49.200
To lure me into your trap,

13:49.920 --> 13:52.440
you have gone to great lengths.

13:53.720 --> 13:54.550
What a pity.

13:57.150 --> 13:58.270
General Qin...

13:58.270 --> 13:58.990
General Qin!

13:58.990 --> 13:59.680
I...

14:00.680 --> 14:01.370
I...

14:14.510 --> 14:15.600
General Qin...

14:16.700 --> 14:18.060
If you kill me now,

14:18.670 --> 14:20.480
you'll never get the formula.

14:21.200 --> 14:22.390
You said before

14:22.510 --> 14:24.240
you only focus on what you want.

14:25.040 --> 14:26.840
And right now,

14:27.400 --> 14:29.460
I'm the only one who knows where it is.

14:29.980 --> 14:31.180
Then what do you want?

14:32.130 --> 14:33.090
I want to live.

14:34.870 --> 14:36.600
Not being a gentleman anymore?

14:37.030 --> 14:38.600
I can't afford to be one now,

14:38.620 --> 14:39.410
can I?

14:43.390 --> 14:44.270
Eleven o'clock

14:44.520 --> 14:45.680
Rongda Casino.

14:46.360 --> 14:47.820
It'll be your last chance.

14:55.060 --> 14:56.350
Just keep waiting.

15:00.030 --> 15:00.790
No.

15:01.240 --> 15:02.840
He's already impatient.

15:03.480 --> 15:04.910
What if the waiting

15:05.480 --> 15:06.550
makes him annoyed

15:07.150 --> 15:08.240
and he leaves?

15:18.390 --> 15:19.600
Ms. Anna,

15:20.550 --> 15:22.440
please come with me.

15:24.180 --> 15:24.900
It's over.

15:25.190 --> 15:27.070
Sun Jiaying works for him.

15:27.470 --> 15:29.400
He's here to settle scores with me.

15:33.390 --> 15:34.120
Apologies,

15:34.140 --> 15:35.100
Ms. Anna.

15:35.800 --> 15:37.890
If you hand over the formula,

15:37.920 --> 15:39.580
perhaps I can spare your life.

15:41.960 --> 15:43.760
Chief Feng, you misunderstood.

15:43.960 --> 15:45.030
You should know

15:45.030 --> 15:46.510
I don't have such a thing.

15:51.080 --> 15:52.240
Ms. Anna,

15:52.550 --> 15:54.810
I know you want to join Qin Xiaoyi's side,

15:55.150 --> 15:56.790
but he's paranoid.

15:57.000 --> 15:58.660
He has so many collaborators.

15:59.120 --> 16:01.000
You're not important to him at all,

16:01.000 --> 16:01.960
Ms. Anna.

16:12.150 --> 16:14.610
Since you refuse to
hand over the formula...

16:15.890 --> 16:16.930
Execute her.

16:22.180 --> 16:23.830
[Economic Cooperation Agreement]

16:22.990 --> 16:30.140
-Big!
-Small!

16:32.030 --> 16:32.670
Again!

17:05.099 --> 17:06.859
I still can't win.

17:39.270 --> 17:40.470
Then what do you want?

17:41.510 --> 17:42.480
I want to live.

17:44.120 --> 17:45.850
Not being a gentleman anymore?

17:45.880 --> 17:47.550
I can't afford to be one now,

17:47.550 --> 17:48.440
can I?

17:58.270 --> 17:59.070
Ms. Anna,

17:59.550 --> 18:00.240
tell me

18:00.880 --> 18:03.050
the formula is still in your possession

18:03.050 --> 18:04.650
and not taken by Feng Youjin.

18:20.240 --> 18:20.920
Of course.

18:34.490 --> 18:36.620
Why did you drop those hawthorn balls?

18:36.800 --> 18:39.200
Were you so certain
I would come to save you?

18:39.920 --> 18:40.790
General Qin,

18:41.070 --> 18:43.270
I wouldn't dare bet on that with you.

18:45.480 --> 18:46.790
I left the hawthorn balls

18:46.790 --> 18:48.030
just to let you know

18:48.550 --> 18:49.880
that I went to the casino

18:49.960 --> 18:51.560
and didn't break my promise.

18:53.510 --> 18:54.770
Did you need to waste
so many hawthorn balls

18:54.770 --> 18:56.770
just to prove you went to the casino?

18:58.830 --> 18:59.750
Ms. Anna,

19:00.680 --> 19:01.810
give me the formula.

19:03.480 --> 19:05.940
And I'll take it as
you keeping your promise.

19:07.640 --> 19:08.370
Don't worry,

19:08.400 --> 19:10.200
I'll take you to get it right now.

19:19.720 --> 19:21.240
After I got the formula,

19:21.750 --> 19:22.640
I hid it

19:22.640 --> 19:25.100
under the container
next to the post office.

19:25.550 --> 19:28.350
The most dangerous place
is also the safest place.

19:30.830 --> 19:31.480
Exactly.

19:34.550 --> 19:35.960
They must have followed us here.

19:35.960 --> 19:37.360
We need to leave quickly.

19:41.640 --> 19:42.590
General Qin,

19:42.890 --> 19:44.680
please hand over the formula.

19:49.520 --> 19:51.280
I did receive a document,

19:51.830 --> 19:52.890
but it doesn't have

19:53.070 --> 19:54.680
your name on it.

19:58.590 --> 20:00.200
It seems what you want

20:00.200 --> 20:02.720
is more than just a simple document.

20:05.110 --> 20:07.570
Since you refuse to
hand over the formula...

20:08.790 --> 20:09.720
Execute her.

20:10.640 --> 20:11.400
Wait!

20:19.000 --> 20:19.750
Chief Feng,

20:20.350 --> 20:22.000
I can ally with anyone,

20:22.850 --> 20:24.720
but the only person I want to defeat

20:24.720 --> 20:26.040
is Qin Xiaoyi.

20:28.000 --> 20:29.350
He knows I have the formula

20:29.350 --> 20:31.260
and will definitely
come looking for me here.

20:31.260 --> 20:32.910
I'll lead him to the formula.

20:34.200 --> 20:36.260
If you want to know where it's hidden,

20:36.660 --> 20:38.180
you should know what to do.

20:40.510 --> 20:41.640
Interesting.

20:47.960 --> 20:48.920
Ms. Anna,

20:49.550 --> 20:50.640
well done.

20:54.720 --> 20:56.270
I was at the end of my rope.

20:56.510 --> 20:59.840
Won't you allow me to
find a way out of a desperate situation?

21:01.680 --> 21:04.000
Finding a way out of
a desperate situation.

21:04.000 --> 21:04.800
Good courage.

21:05.130 --> 21:06.130
I miscalculated.

21:07.640 --> 21:09.200
But the game isn't over yet.

21:09.480 --> 21:10.810
I hope in today's match,

21:11.070 --> 21:12.600
you'll have the last laugh.

21:12.830 --> 21:13.640
I will.

21:14.600 --> 21:16.640
When the mayor's election comes,

21:16.660 --> 21:19.390
I invite you to sit in the audience
and see clearly

21:19.530 --> 21:21.260
who the final winner really is.

21:21.680 --> 21:24.240
♪ Think about you ♪

21:24.070 --> 21:24.790
Take him away.

21:24.540 --> 21:26.580
♪ Care about you ♪

21:26.610 --> 21:28.610
♪ Goodnight to you ♪

21:29.200 --> 21:31.580
♪ All night long for you ♪

21:31.740 --> 21:34.080
♪ Think about you ♪

21:34.320 --> 21:36.730
♪ Care about you ♪

21:35.200 --> 21:36.550
Ning Zechen and his team

21:36.550 --> 21:38.480
won the final victory!

21:37.220 --> 21:38.730
♪ Goodnight to you ♪

21:39.130 --> 21:41.700
♪ All night long for you ♪

21:42.320 --> 21:43.910
♪ Think about you ♪

21:44.290 --> 21:46.340
♪ Care about you ♪

21:46.940 --> 21:48.940
♪ Goodnight to you ♪

21:49.550 --> 21:52.100
♪ All night long for you ♪

21:50.880 --> 21:51.750
Where is he?

21:52.130 --> 21:54.130
♪ Think about you ♪

21:54.310 --> 21:57.100
♪ All night long for you ♪

21:55.270 --> 21:56.110
Today is Member's Day.

21:56.110 --> 21:56.750
Free water available.

21:56.750 --> 21:57.680
Please help yourselves.

21:57.680 --> 22:00.240
Remember to replenish electrolytes
after exercising.

22:00.240 --> 22:01.270
What's this for?

22:01.590 --> 22:02.200
This?

22:02.200 --> 22:02.960
It's for you to leave messages

22:02.960 --> 22:04.440
for your favorite NPC.

22:05.160 --> 22:06.510
Although we don't recommend

22:06.510 --> 22:07.440
players and NPCs

22:07.440 --> 22:08.680
having too much off-game contact,

22:08.680 --> 22:10.070
you can use this method

22:10.070 --> 22:11.930
to express your support and love.

22:12.960 --> 22:14.960
I can only express my support and love?

22:14.960 --> 22:18.360
It's not appropriate
to write negative comments here, is it?

22:22.830 --> 22:23.440
Thank you.

22:27.460 --> 22:29.240
[The fox can't be the winner here. -Anna]

22:38.640 --> 22:40.310
[Mr. Xu]

23:01.590 --> 23:02.240
Mr. Xu.

23:03.000 --> 23:05.060
Why did you suddenly cancel my leave?

23:05.070 --> 23:07.200
Do we have a new client?

23:07.550 --> 23:08.830
It's not a new client.

23:08.920 --> 23:09.440
We have

23:09.750 --> 23:11.350
a new team member joining us.

23:12.480 --> 23:13.810
Come here, Shuaishuai.

23:13.960 --> 23:14.680
Shuaishuai.

23:14.680 --> 23:15.920
Come here.

23:16.440 --> 23:18.770
I've noticed you're quite free every day.

23:19.070 --> 23:21.270
Take it to the pet salon this afternoon.

23:21.960 --> 23:23.160
Come, come.

23:24.720 --> 23:25.400
Good.

23:27.830 --> 23:28.510
Mr. Xu.

23:29.310 --> 23:31.640
I joined the company right after college.

23:32.410 --> 23:34.610
I originally wanted to
be an architect.

23:35.000 --> 23:36.960
You said you needed

23:37.070 --> 23:39.000
an assistant who understood architecture,

23:39.000 --> 23:40.790
so you had me fill the spot temporarily

23:40.790 --> 23:42.550
and said you'd transfer me
to the design department later.

23:42.550 --> 23:43.350
That's right.

23:44.510 --> 23:45.770
It's been three years.

23:46.240 --> 23:47.920
What about that transfer?

23:50.070 --> 23:50.830
Hu.

23:52.400 --> 23:53.920
That's not the right way to put it.

23:53.920 --> 23:55.650
I've already transferred you.

23:56.000 --> 23:56.860
Think about it.

23:56.940 --> 23:58.470
You used to be an assistant.

23:58.590 --> 23:59.440
And now?

23:59.940 --> 24:02.360
You're the general manager's assistant.

24:02.830 --> 24:03.510
Right?

24:05.750 --> 24:06.750
Isn't that right?

24:17.640 --> 24:18.270
Hu.

24:20.190 --> 24:21.110
The company

24:21.130 --> 24:22.610
doesn't have many projects now.

24:22.610 --> 24:24.740
We don't need designers at the moment.

24:25.400 --> 24:26.030
Wait until we secure

24:26.030 --> 24:26.960
another big client this year—

24:26.960 --> 24:29.200
"Once we secure
a few more big clients this year,

24:29.200 --> 24:30.400
"I'll definitely transfer you.

24:30.400 --> 24:32.400
"Young people shouldn't be too impatient,

24:32.400 --> 24:34.460
"or you'll end up at a disadvantage."

24:38.520 --> 24:39.980
What are you trying to say?

24:40.940 --> 24:41.730
Nothing.

24:42.310 --> 24:43.510
As your assistant,

24:43.680 --> 24:44.750
I take to heart

24:44.750 --> 24:46.350
everything you say.

24:49.960 --> 24:50.960
I'll head out now.

24:58.490 --> 24:59.940
I was at the end of my rope.

25:00.160 --> 25:02.790
Won't you allow me to
find a way out of a desperate situation?

25:02.790 --> 25:04.160
I hope in today's game,

25:04.470 --> 25:06.000
you'll have the last laugh.

25:07.400 --> 25:07.960
Mr. Xu.

25:10.200 --> 25:11.110
What is it now?

25:11.880 --> 25:12.790
I'm quitting.

25:14.200 --> 25:15.240
Quitting?

25:16.840 --> 25:18.670
Before I quit, let me warn you:

25:18.850 --> 25:20.750
it's best not to drink that coffee.

25:20.750 --> 25:23.330
Last month, several employees
in our department said

25:23.330 --> 25:25.880
they found dead cockroaches
when cleaning the coffee machine.

25:25.880 --> 25:26.740
How many was it?

25:27.070 --> 25:29.160
Two or three?

25:30.880 --> 25:33.410
Hu, why didn't you
tell me about this earlier?

25:37.080 --> 25:39.080
I think there were four, Mr. Xu!

25:48.160 --> 25:49.000
Zhao,

25:49.000 --> 25:51.130
I was just using that to fool my boss...

25:51.340 --> 25:52.720
No, my former boss.

25:52.750 --> 25:54.610
Why do you actually believe that?

25:55.920 --> 25:56.880
Hu Xiu, how did I never notice

25:56.880 --> 25:58.920
that you're actually crazy?

26:00.480 --> 26:01.240
Crazy?

26:01.480 --> 26:02.680
I love that title.

26:02.880 --> 26:04.410
Thanks for the compliment.

26:05.510 --> 26:08.570
So you've decided to quit
without another job lined up?

26:09.790 --> 26:11.680
You don't have any backup plans
for yourself.

26:11.680 --> 26:15.410
It would be so much better
if you found another job before quitting.

26:18.000 --> 26:18.750
Zhao.

26:20.270 --> 26:23.670
Do you know what happens to someone
who stays with a bad option

26:23.920 --> 26:25.650
while looking for better ones?

26:27.350 --> 26:28.940
They end up spending their whole life

26:28.940 --> 26:31.200
on that bad option without realizing it.

26:31.510 --> 26:32.400
So,

26:32.400 --> 26:33.720
I have to push myself

26:34.440 --> 26:35.750
to start over fresh.

26:37.160 --> 26:38.510
Start over fresh?

26:39.160 --> 26:40.480
You mean...

26:42.590 --> 26:44.480
I still want to be an architect.

26:46.510 --> 26:47.240
Are you sure?

26:49.030 --> 26:50.030
Then I support you

26:50.510 --> 26:52.270
with all my heart.

26:55.720 --> 26:57.110
You're so strong.

26:57.640 --> 26:59.070
You're just too weak.

26:59.920 --> 27:00.590
Who is it?

27:01.400 --> 27:02.310
Don't look.

27:02.890 --> 27:04.150
A murder mystery game?

27:04.290 --> 27:05.950
There's a game in half an hour.

27:06.790 --> 27:08.920
Going again? Didn't you win last time?

27:10.260 --> 27:12.460
The fox didn't witness it last time.

27:12.960 --> 27:14.550
It wasn't a perfect victory.

27:14.550 --> 27:15.110
I'm off.

27:18.960 --> 27:19.920
Fox?

27:21.440 --> 27:22.880
Is that a new character?

27:28.510 --> 27:29.440
This way please.

27:30.810 --> 27:36.680
♪ Life lays out the outline of my scenes ♪

27:35.720 --> 27:36.550
So beautiful.

27:37.910 --> 27:41.390
♪ The last act
was a monologue in a dream ♪

27:42.590 --> 27:46.360
♪ And in the next,
I wander through the city's noise ♪

27:47.520 --> 27:50.580
♪ So many arrivals
that turned out to be nothing ♪

27:52.010 --> 27:56.080
♪ I'm counting the beats of the clock ♪

27:56.640 --> 28:00.580
♪ I can't tell which platform
is for leaving or returning ♪

28:01.250 --> 28:05.540
♪ Until you walk toward me ♪

28:02.270 --> 28:03.330
Everyone, welcome

28:03.920 --> 28:05.070
to Rongcheng.

28:14.510 --> 28:15.770
[Group B Warlord Commander Qin Xiaoyi]

28:27.240 --> 28:29.140
The current situation in Rongcheng

28:29.140 --> 28:30.770
is extremely complicated.

28:32.200 --> 28:32.960
Chief Feng

28:33.700 --> 28:36.570
has already established cooperation
with Pavlovich,

28:36.570 --> 28:39.770
while Director Lin
has Mr. Kobayashi backing him.

28:40.110 --> 28:40.830
Anna,

28:41.920 --> 28:42.750
today,

28:43.110 --> 28:45.440
if we can reach an agreement

28:45.790 --> 28:48.680
and I get the support
from M's headquarters,

28:49.090 --> 28:49.770
then I

28:51.110 --> 28:52.960
will definitely lead you

28:53.510 --> 28:55.000
to ultimate victory.

28:59.270 --> 29:00.000
Anna!

29:00.390 --> 29:02.940
This Qin Xiaoyi is so over-the-top.

29:07.070 --> 29:07.960
Ms. Anna.

29:14.030 --> 29:14.720
I'm sorry.

29:14.880 --> 29:16.000
I'll think about

29:16.200 --> 29:17.110
this cooperation some more.

29:17.110 --> 29:18.480
Anna, Anna!

29:18.960 --> 29:20.640
I don't think you understand what I mean.

29:20.640 --> 29:21.480
If you have any concerns,

29:21.480 --> 29:23.240
feel free to bring them up.

29:24.280 --> 29:25.680
We will achieve victory.

29:26.590 --> 29:27.480
Trust me.

29:31.830 --> 29:32.830
This contract...

29:34.490 --> 29:35.580
You can take it.

29:36.000 --> 29:37.310
But, General Qin,

29:37.720 --> 29:39.110
being too eager

29:39.320 --> 29:41.430
only makes me doubt your abilities.

29:49.160 --> 29:51.160
If you want me to sign this contract,

29:51.590 --> 29:53.590
you need to show me your sincerity.

29:56.130 --> 29:56.930
Wait a minute.

29:58.550 --> 30:00.750
I don't quite understand what you mean.

30:01.350 --> 30:03.750
What kind of sincerity
are you looking for?

30:10.070 --> 30:11.960
How many candied hawthorns
would I need to eat

30:11.960 --> 30:13.960
to make the 600 yuan worth it?

30:16.050 --> 30:17.140
Let me go!

30:17.170 --> 30:20.080
I've been framed! I've been framed!

30:20.590 --> 30:21.240
Anna,

30:21.440 --> 30:22.970
I'm so disappointed in you!

30:23.000 --> 30:25.070
I'm so disappointed in you!

30:25.240 --> 30:26.400
Anna!

30:26.470 --> 30:27.710
Likewise.

30:40.940 --> 30:41.490
Hello.

30:42.240 --> 30:43.590
How come today's Qin Xiaoyi

30:43.590 --> 30:45.350
is different from before?

30:45.790 --> 30:47.310
We have two groups of actors, A and B.

30:47.310 --> 30:48.710
They perform in rotation.

30:48.710 --> 30:49.830
I see.

30:50.350 --> 30:52.610
Do you have a schedule for the two groups?

30:53.370 --> 30:54.240
Yes, we do,

30:54.550 --> 30:56.350
but the actor you want to see

30:56.350 --> 30:57.770
is our special guest performer.

30:57.770 --> 30:59.500
His work schedule is not fixed.

30:59.770 --> 31:01.570
I don't know the details either.

31:02.800 --> 31:03.430
Take care.

31:18.270 --> 31:20.470
These aren't the same messages as before.

31:20.470 --> 31:21.470
That makes sense.

31:21.530 --> 31:24.460
They'll run out of room
if they don't switch them out.

31:52.000 --> 31:53.510
Can it read my mind?

31:53.510 --> 31:55.770
Does anyone know Qin Xiaoyi's real name?

31:55.880 --> 31:57.510
All the other NPC actors
created social media accounts.

31:57.510 --> 31:58.920
Only he's being mysterious.

31:58.920 --> 32:00.920
He's not even on the official cast list.

32:00.920 --> 32:02.510
I have a friend who used to work there.

32:02.510 --> 32:03.830
Even he couldn't find any information.

32:03.830 --> 32:05.750
They say he doesn't like public attention.

32:05.750 --> 32:06.720
He's just an NPC actor.

32:06.720 --> 32:07.830
It's not like he's some big celebrity.

32:07.830 --> 32:08.880
Why be so mysterious?

32:08.880 --> 32:10.480
Probably just a marketing strategy.

32:10.480 --> 32:12.000
Whether it's a strategy or not,

32:12.000 --> 32:13.790
the other actor is really not as good.

32:13.790 --> 32:14.750
Indeed,

32:15.070 --> 32:16.400
he's not quite as good.

32:21.200 --> 32:21.880
Mr. Gong,

32:22.200 --> 32:23.800
I need to tell you something.

32:24.170 --> 32:26.920
Qin Xiaoyi from Group A
hasn't been coming these days.

32:26.920 --> 32:27.920
Today, there was even a player

32:27.920 --> 32:30.370
who specifically asked about his sessions.

32:30.370 --> 32:31.850
Okay, I got it.

32:34.680 --> 32:35.720
Hello, sir.

32:35.830 --> 32:37.290
Do you have a reservation?

32:37.510 --> 32:38.070
Yes,

32:38.530 --> 32:39.930
I'm waiting for a friend.

32:44.720 --> 32:45.310
Mr. Xiao.

32:46.270 --> 32:46.960
My friend.

32:47.150 --> 32:48.150
This way, please.

32:48.960 --> 32:50.490
Been quite busy these days?

32:50.890 --> 32:52.750
Looking for apartments everywhere.

32:52.750 --> 32:54.640
No wonder you haven't been to the club.

32:54.640 --> 32:55.790
Wait, if you're looking for apartments,

32:55.790 --> 32:57.510
you can just have your agent
do the legwork.

32:57.510 --> 32:59.170
Why are you going personally?

32:59.920 --> 33:02.120
The rental situation there is special.

33:02.880 --> 33:04.680
There are a lot of shared spaces.

33:05.400 --> 33:08.260
The landlords want to
meet tenants before renting.

33:12.030 --> 33:12.830
What's wrong?

33:15.480 --> 33:16.680
I know you're busy.

33:16.870 --> 33:19.200
You can come to the club
whenever you want.

33:19.310 --> 33:20.310
It's just that...

33:20.350 --> 33:21.880
An employee just called me.

33:21.920 --> 33:23.000
He said there was a player today

33:23.000 --> 33:24.200
who specifically asked about Qin Xiaoyi

33:24.200 --> 33:26.110
and the schedule for Groups A and B.

33:26.110 --> 33:27.970
Seems like they came just for you.

33:28.270 --> 33:29.880
I'm just mentioning it.

33:30.620 --> 33:31.880
But Xiao, don't worry.

33:32.310 --> 33:34.070
When we first opened this club,

33:34.070 --> 33:35.270
we agreed on everything.

33:35.270 --> 33:36.770
It absolutely won't affect your work.

33:36.770 --> 33:39.270
Your schedule and information
are completely confidential.

33:39.270 --> 33:41.420
You won't have any private contact
with players.

33:41.420 --> 33:42.220
Rest assured.

33:53.440 --> 33:55.750
Take a good look

33:57.240 --> 33:59.440
who the final winner really is.

34:01.860 --> 34:05.790
[Qin Xiaoyi]

34:09.550 --> 34:10.949
This is no problem at all.

34:12.480 --> 34:13.320
Sure, sure.

34:15.840 --> 34:16.770
It's just ahead.

34:21.360 --> 34:21.889
This way.

34:24.280 --> 34:25.150
Granny Chen.

34:26.070 --> 34:26.880
Granny Chen!

34:27.500 --> 34:29.900
I've brought a client
to see the apartment.

34:31.810 --> 34:32.480
Excuse us.

34:32.960 --> 34:33.710
Come in.

34:41.670 --> 34:42.320
Thank you.

34:45.760 --> 34:46.110
Here, watch your step.

34:46.110 --> 34:46.920
It's fine.

34:48.000 --> 34:49.150
Alright, it's fine.

34:49.400 --> 34:50.960
The path is uneven. Take it slow.

34:50.960 --> 34:51.920
Okay, don't worry.

34:51.920 --> 34:52.480
Don't worry about me.

34:52.480 --> 34:53.070
Just hold onto your things.

34:53.070 --> 34:54.230
Coming to see Xiu?

34:54.400 --> 34:55.130
You're back?

34:55.550 --> 34:56.110
Yes, yes.

34:56.840 --> 34:57.440
Watch out.

34:58.230 --> 34:59.560
Where should I put this?

35:02.510 --> 35:03.280
Young man,

35:03.590 --> 35:05.650
how long are you planning to rent for?

35:06.550 --> 35:07.480
I haven't decided yet,

35:07.480 --> 35:09.010
so I'd like to rent by month.

35:10.630 --> 35:11.630
Take it easy.

35:12.760 --> 35:13.110
In...

35:14.360 --> 35:15.190
Ex-in-law.

35:16.750 --> 35:17.520
Don't call us that.

35:17.520 --> 35:19.120
We don't deserve that title.

35:21.320 --> 35:22.360
Is Xiu not here?

35:23.520 --> 35:25.390
So, you're living in this house now?

35:25.390 --> 35:27.100
This is all my family's property!

35:27.100 --> 35:29.500
Why should an outsider
care who lives here?

35:29.960 --> 35:31.630
I'm just asking if she's here.

35:31.630 --> 35:32.830
Why are you shouting?

35:33.090 --> 35:33.970
Don't worry.

35:34.150 --> 35:36.550
Living here
is very convenient and comfortable.

35:36.550 --> 35:38.400
All the neighbors
have been here for years.

35:38.400 --> 35:39.510
Everyone gets along well with each other.

35:39.510 --> 35:41.030
First, get that irresponsible son of yours

35:41.030 --> 35:42.110
to come back to Shanghai

35:42.110 --> 35:43.150
and apologize in person.

35:43.150 --> 35:44.180
What do you mean irresponsible?

35:44.180 --> 35:45.580
What's wrong with my son?

35:46.360 --> 35:48.070
Is breaking up being irresponsible?

35:48.070 --> 35:49.400
These days, people date

35:49.400 --> 35:51.130
and break up all the time, okay?

35:51.710 --> 35:53.110
What was he doing before this?

35:53.110 --> 35:54.760
Did he have to do it at this point?

35:54.760 --> 35:56.630
And now, he's not even coming back.

35:56.630 --> 35:57.960
What kind of man is that?

35:58.070 --> 35:58.960
Alright, alright.

35:58.960 --> 36:00.160
Keep your voice down.

36:00.440 --> 36:02.040
The neighbors are watching.

36:06.280 --> 36:07.000
Well,

36:07.030 --> 36:07.990
Normally,

36:08.020 --> 36:10.620
the soundproofing
is quite effective, right?

36:11.630 --> 36:13.280
That's Mr. Hu's daughter.

36:13.420 --> 36:15.040
She was planning to get married,

36:15.040 --> 36:16.170
but for some reason,

36:16.170 --> 36:18.570
the groom ran away
on their engagement day.

36:18.590 --> 36:19.440
If you ask me,

36:19.440 --> 36:20.350
she's right to yell at him.

36:20.350 --> 36:21.680
Um, Granny,

36:21.710 --> 36:23.710
this is a special situation, right?

36:24.590 --> 36:26.630
It's not usually this noisy.

36:27.080 --> 36:28.680
It's not like this normally.

36:32.720 --> 36:34.650
Your son broke off the engagement!

36:35.280 --> 36:38.110
And you have the nerve
to come to our house, demanding answers

36:38.110 --> 36:40.440
and wanting the first-meeting gift back?

36:40.440 --> 36:41.960
I've never seen anything like this.

36:41.960 --> 36:43.150
Let's break up peacefully

36:43.150 --> 36:44.410
and part on good terms.

36:44.440 --> 36:45.070
What's wrong with

36:45.070 --> 36:46.550
settling accounts clearly?

36:46.550 --> 36:48.020
Or would you like everyone
to judge who's right?

36:48.020 --> 36:48.620
Hey!

36:48.840 --> 36:49.590
Mom, Dad.

36:50.400 --> 36:51.400
Xiu, you're here.

36:52.550 --> 36:53.410
Don't be angry.

36:53.440 --> 36:54.070
Go inside.

36:54.360 --> 36:55.290
I'll talk to her.

36:55.480 --> 36:56.400
Calm down.

36:56.400 --> 36:57.810
Getting angry is bad for your health.

36:57.810 --> 36:59.010
Come inside quickly.

37:01.230 --> 37:02.000
Auntie,

37:02.490 --> 37:05.000
if you want
the first-meeting gift money back,

37:05.000 --> 37:05.730
that's fine.

37:06.190 --> 37:07.320
But I remember

37:07.320 --> 37:09.550
when my parents first met Zhang Qiran,

37:09.760 --> 37:11.360
they also gave him a gift

37:11.360 --> 37:12.920
based on what you gave me.

37:13.510 --> 37:14.550
Both sides are even,

37:14.550 --> 37:15.940
yet you're demanding money today.

37:15.940 --> 37:17.340
What's the logic in that?

37:18.250 --> 37:19.630
That was received by Qiran.

37:19.630 --> 37:20.440
It never went through my hands.

37:20.440 --> 37:22.240
What about the engagement banquet?

37:22.240 --> 37:23.840
You don't argue about that.

37:24.630 --> 37:25.850
My parents upgraded the venue.

37:25.850 --> 37:28.230
You didn't even mention the cost
and that's fine,

37:28.230 --> 37:29.510
but you immediately added

37:29.510 --> 37:31.440
another table for your relatives.

37:32.080 --> 37:33.670
She has the nerve to ask for money?

37:33.670 --> 37:34.200
Exactly.

37:34.800 --> 37:35.880
You seem

37:35.880 --> 37:37.590
more pitiful than me,

37:37.760 --> 37:38.840
who got dumped.

37:39.070 --> 37:40.280
I will never have
anything to do with your son

37:40.280 --> 37:41.800
for the rest of my life.

37:42.740 --> 37:44.400
But you and that kind of person

37:45.110 --> 37:47.370
will probably be tied together forever.

37:50.590 --> 37:51.320
Auntie,

37:51.840 --> 37:53.500
I'll see you out one last time.

38:03.960 --> 38:06.190
If you're looking for a short-term rental,

38:06.190 --> 38:07.800
it's indeed a bit troublesome.

38:07.800 --> 38:09.190
As soon as I hear from Granny Chen,

38:09.190 --> 38:10.920
I'll let you know immediately.

38:11.590 --> 38:12.190
Okay.

38:13.760 --> 38:14.590
Please move.

38:24.280 --> 38:25.280
Xiu!

38:25.760 --> 38:26.590
Coming.

38:35.150 --> 38:36.590
Oh, please.

38:36.590 --> 38:38.320
Control your temper, will you?

38:38.320 --> 38:40.070
Xiu lives here.

38:40.070 --> 38:41.110
If you make a scene everywhere,

38:41.110 --> 38:42.920
how can she continue living here?

38:42.920 --> 38:43.920
Really.

38:45.630 --> 38:46.550
Mom, Dad.

38:46.960 --> 38:47.760
I'm sorry.

38:48.030 --> 38:49.290
It's all because of me.

38:49.960 --> 38:51.070
That's not right.

38:51.480 --> 38:52.710
How could this be your fault?

38:52.710 --> 38:54.230
It's like walking down the street

38:54.230 --> 38:56.230
and stepping in dog poop
someone left behind.

38:56.230 --> 38:58.630
You can't blame yourself
for your bad luck.

38:58.630 --> 38:59.990
We're eating here.

39:01.630 --> 39:02.760
Fine, I'll stop talking.

39:02.760 --> 39:03.280
Here.

39:03.640 --> 39:04.500
Have some soup.

39:04.590 --> 39:05.670
Come sit down.

39:08.920 --> 39:10.670
You should go back to work now.

39:10.920 --> 39:12.590
You can't stay on vacation
at home forever.

39:12.590 --> 39:13.590
This isn't right.

39:13.670 --> 39:14.440
Besides,

39:14.440 --> 39:15.510
no matter what,

39:15.670 --> 39:18.400
your current job is quite stable.

39:19.190 --> 39:21.070
We'll find you an even better man later.

39:21.070 --> 39:22.710
He'll definitely be better
than that Zhang guy.

39:22.710 --> 39:23.220
Right?

39:23.250 --> 39:23.960
Dad,

39:24.550 --> 39:26.210
actually, I've already qu...

39:26.320 --> 39:27.120
What's wrong?

39:27.480 --> 39:28.110
It hurts.

39:28.660 --> 39:31.120
I think it's going to rain
in a couple of days.

39:32.670 --> 39:34.190
What did you just say?

39:34.190 --> 39:35.030
What's wrong?

39:36.880 --> 39:39.060
I've made up my mind.

39:39.120 --> 39:41.560
I'm fine. I'll work hard.

39:46.550 --> 39:48.240
I just saw my parents off.

39:48.670 --> 39:50.670
My mom brought you some side dishes.

39:51.000 --> 39:52.070
Thank her for me.

39:52.230 --> 39:54.360
I guess they're finally relieved now.

39:55.630 --> 39:56.840
Did you tell them

39:57.070 --> 39:58.400
about your job?

39:59.880 --> 40:00.840
It's okay.

40:01.030 --> 40:03.070
Once you find a new job in a few days,

40:03.070 --> 40:04.930
they won't say anything about it.

40:05.230 --> 40:07.150
I have to go to
the park managers' meeting tonight.

40:07.150 --> 40:08.150
Talk to you later.

40:16.460 --> 40:21.570
♪ I saw the tram
driving under the sunset ♪

40:24.120 --> 40:29.130
♪ Like walking into a pause in a summer ♪

40:24.480 --> 40:26.840
The distance of the glass wall
needs to be recalculated.

40:26.840 --> 40:28.510
Send me the 3D model tomorrow.

40:30.880 --> 40:33.890
♪ At this moment, the sunset is gentle ♪

40:34.690 --> 40:37.340
♪ I look up and press the shutter ♪

40:38.710 --> 40:45.840
♪ I take a bit of your city as a memory ♪

40:46.590 --> 40:47.230
Mr. Xiao.

40:46.830 --> 40:51.640
♪ I take a bit of your city as a memory ♪

40:48.550 --> 40:49.920
The technical director is over there.

40:49.920 --> 40:50.630
Follow me.

40:54.030 --> 40:59.150
♪ Leaving a hurried silhouette
for the dusk ♪

41:01.010 --> 41:04.360
♪ Talking about random topics ♪

41:04.600 --> 41:08.020
♪ Waiting for the traffic light at dusk ♪
